{"tid":677812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普對朝鮮最新回應表歡迎：溫暖有建設性，是大好消息","createTime":"2018-05-25T13:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T14:26:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88a010a368f701d42c2503f49983a26d82704cec","tid":677812,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"簡訊：特朗普對朝鮮最新談話表歡迎<br />\n韓聯社首爾5月25日電 美國總統特朗普當地時間25日在推特發帖評價稱，朝鮮外務省第一副相金桂官前日的談話是溫暖而有建設性的談話，是大好消息。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普表示，我們即將看到這能否發展為持續的繁榮與和平，只有時間（還有手腕）會給出答案。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普前日發出公開信，以朝方言論展現出極大的憤怒和公然的敵意為由取消原定於下月12日的朝美首腦會談。金桂官隨後發表談話予以回應，與他16日的談話相比，措辭克制語調緩和，釋放出繼續對話的意願。 （完）"},{"pid":"0d6113307a06d8fbb9ea770795c4a442af74037a","tid":677812,"uid":17980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚狗"},{"pid":"ae30da3f08dcd66aa8b94e9dfcf1e8a6accd759a","tid":677812,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真，有冇英文source?"},{"pid":"3191c7868f12acf39a9d6c7f589b7132f452299f","tid":677812,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/999986971660423170?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F999986971660423170%3Fs%3D19&d=cbF0bS4pKh3BDNQfrBLWC%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=248606ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F999986971660423170%3Fs%3D19&h=d8b00eec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/999986971660423170?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"26b548eb2f6d7f5d458447960944a230c75b22e6","tid":677812,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"Very good news to receive the warm and